(1410, 1, 'admin/aboutus/1', 'PUT', '192.168.1.51', '{\"name\":\"about us\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"companyprofiletag\":\"COMPANY PROFILE  THE GROUP (SINCE 1996)\",\"companyprofiledescription\":\"<div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n                    <p>RamaPly is today an eminent and trusted name in the Indian domestic panel industry. It has been 50 years since our foray began in 1964. In fact, we take pride in the fact that consistent and dedicated efforts, along with innovative techniques and approach that spans decades, has resulted in the success of Rama Group of companies. With an annual turn over of INR 700 Cr, we stand tall as the leading manufacturer of Steel, Film Face Shuttering Plywood, Flush Doors, Door Frames and Timber Trading, in India. <\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>Rama Group of companies includes Rama Wood Crafts (ISO 9001:2008) and Rama Panels Pvt. Ltd. (ISO 9001:2008), with three business divisions: Wood Based, Iron and Steel and Timber. The state-of-the-art production facilities, dedicated research and development unit, able leadership and dedicated team are calibrated as a cohesive whole, to scale greater heights of success.   <\\/p>\\r\\n                <\\/div>\\r\\n<h5>Rama Wood Craft<\\/h5>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n                    <p>Found in 1996, Rama Wood Craft is an ISO 9001: 2008 certified company that produces exceptional quality BIS certified products. The manufacturing plants are equipped with hi-tech machinery to ensure finesse in the final product. The plant is situated in Satna district of Madhya Pradesh which is renowned for rich hardwood. The chief products are different grades of plywood, block boards, flush doors and particle boards.  <\\/p>\\r\\n                <\\/div>\\r\\n<h5>Rama Panels Pvt. Ltd.<\\/h5>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n<p>Established in 2007, Rama Panels has an ultra modern manufacturing facility in Rudrapur, Uttarakhand. It is an ISO 9001: 2008 accredited company with a plant that sprawls over 15 acres of land. Proximity to raw materials of the best quality ensures ease in procurement and production of the finest goods. All the products are certified by BIS and Forest Stewardship Council. The company is also a member of the Indian Green Building Council. <\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"visionmissiontag\":\"Vision & Mission Taking Life Ahead\",\"missionvisiondescription\":\"<p>To be an exemplary model in the infrastructure industry that offers the world, premium and incredible range of products. We will achieve this goal through synchronised hard work, integrity and innovation at all levels. <\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>Our mission is to manufacture and make accessible superior quality, innovative products at affordable prices, thereby winning the trust of a global network of client\\u00e8le. <\\/p>\",\"ourteamdescription\":\"<span>\\\"Remember, teamwork begins by building trust. And the only way to do that is to overcome our need for invulnerability.\\\" <br>\\r\\n-Patrick Lencioni \\r\\n<\\/span>\\r\\n                <div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n                    <p>Trust is the foundation of our team. Faith in the vision of the leadership, coupled with the expertise of the team, and their tenacity to towards the common goal enables us to achieve seemingly impossible feats. It is this promise and realisation of consistent success that prompts the team members to work with us for an average of 10 years.  <\\/p>\\r\\n                <\\/div>\",\"aboutushomedescription\":\"<h3>The Rama Group of companies is a leading member of the Indian domestic panel industry.<\\/h3>\\r\\n                <div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n                    <p>Since the Group\'s inception, we have always planned for the future with a highly dedicated team and achieved our ambitious goals with the help of a hi-tech infrastructure and result oriented after sales service.<\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>We have marketing offices all over India.<\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>The Rama Group consists of two companies - Rama Wood Craft and Rama Panels Private Limited.<\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>The unit is ISO 9001:2000 certified and is well reputed in the<\\/p>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"#\\\">Read More<\\/a>\\r\\n                <\\/div>\",\"infrastructuretag\":\"Infrastructure Taking Life Ahead\",\"infrastructuredescription\":\"<p>We have two state-of-art facilities: in Satna district of Madhya Pradesh, and Rudrapur town of Uttarakhand. Both the units are located close to sources of rich hardwood and best quality timber. The proximity creates ease in procurement of raw materials and production of final goods.<\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>The facilities have modern and exclusively dedicated units that execute processes to deliver exceptional quality at each stage. Some of these units are: core veneer section, fork lift, cold press, calibrator, peeling machine, etc. The manual work is carried out by trained manpower under stringent supervision of techno-quality staff. <\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"l3mpPiRgn78kULWIprqMAtjRN7JSjF4kYYVHdTRh\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"http:\\/\\/192.168.1.251\\/ramaply\\/public\\/admin\\/aboutus\"}', '2019-06-13 10:39:58', '2019-06-13 10:39:58'),
